OL,7,FIf the trial is successful, the
OL,8,Fconcept could be rolled out more
OL,9,Fwidely, ITV News' Amy Lewis explains
OL,11,FFour Women's Championship teams are
OL,12,Fset to take part in a pilot scheme
OL,13,Fthat will allow supporters to drink
OL,14,Falcohol in the stands.
OL,16,FStarting this month, Southampton,
OL,17,FNewcastle, Bristol, and Birmingham
OL,18,Fwill trial the programme, the clubs
OL,19,Fhave announced.
