OL,3,CFour Women's Championship teams to
OL,4,Callow fans to drink alcohol in the
OL,5,Cstands
OL,7,FThe clubs were partly selected due to
OL,8,Ftheir geographical spread but also
OL,9,Fbecause their venues are accustomed to
OL,10,Fallowing alcohol to be consumed by
OL,11,Ffans.
OL,13,FUnder the Sporting Events Act of 1985,
OL,14,Fdrinking in the stands is currently
OL,15,Fbanned in the top five tiers of the
OL,16,FEnglish men's game - but the
OL,17,Flegislation does not cover the women's
OL,18,Fgame.
