OL,7,FIf the trial is successful, the
OL,8,Fconcept could be rolled out more
OL,9,Fwidely across the Women's Super League
OL,10,Fand Women's Championship.
OL,12,FDirector of Women's Football for
OL,13,FSouthampton FC Marieanne Spacey-Cale
OL,14,Fsaid the trial "marks an exciting step
OL,15,Fin enhancing the matchday experience
OL,16,Ffor our fans."
