OL,7,F"By allowing alcohol to be consumed
OL,8,Fresponsibly in the bowl, we aim to
OL,9,Fcreate an inclusive, enjoyable
OL,10,Fatmosphere that mirrors the vibrant
OL,11,Fenergy of the sport itself.
