OL,3,CFour Women's Championship teams to
OL,4,Callow fans to drink alcohol in the
OL,5,Cstands
OL,7,F"Whilst we know it might not be
OL,8,Feveryone; this trial is about offering
OL,9,Ffans the choice to have a drink whilst
OL,10,Fwatching the game if they'd like to,"
OL,11,Fshe added.
OL,13,FNewcastle United also said in a
OL,14,Fstatement that it will continue "to
OL,15,Flook at ways to improve the matchday
OL,16,Fexperience of fans" while Birmingham
OL,17,Fsaid it will review the scheme until
OL,18,Fthe end of the season "before a
OL,19,Fpermanent decision is made."
