OL,7,FBristol Sport CEO and Bristol City
OL,8,FWomen Board Chair Gavin Marshall said:
OL,9,F"We believe that fans being allowed to
OL,10,Fenjoy their refreshment of choice in
OL,11,Fview of the pitch will add to what is
OL,12,Falready a great matchday experience."
OL,14,FEach team will be involved with the
OL,15,Fpilot for either four or five home
OL,16,Ffixtures in the second half of the
OL,17,FWomen's Championship season.
