OL,7,FBoth Bristol City and Southampton will
OL,8,Fbegin on January 19 during their games
OL,9,Fagainst London City Lionesses and
OL,10,FSunderland, respectively.
OL,12,FBirmingham and Newcastle will trial
OL,13,Fthe scheme the following week in their
OL,14,Fhome fixtures on January 26 against
OL,15,FBristol City and Portsmouth,
OL,16,Frespectively.
